      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.cQtmz297P5g6g5xv]{Advanced Mods}</p>\n<p>Once per day as a standard action, your drone can turn invisible for 10 minutes, as per the <em>invisibility</em> spell @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.YDXegEus8p0BnsH1]{Invisibility}. If it makes an attack during this time, the invisibility ends. Your drone can spend 2 Resolve Points to use this ability again on the same day. Your drone must have the reactive camouflage mod @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.ZCNA7qg5Hz6Jirs0]{Reactive Camouflage (Ex; Drone)} to select this.</p>"
